column1: # The "setting" column can take one of the following values
# 0  => Tunnel waypoint FLY direct; with roll/pitch/heading
# 1  => Tunnel waypoint FLY direct; with roll/pitch/heading no RECTANGLE draw
# 2  => Tunnel waypoint FLY direct; with roll/pitch/heading no LINE draw
# 10 => Tunnel waypoint FLY direct; only trajectory points
# 11 => Tunnel waypoint FLY direct; only trajectory points no RECTANGLE draw
# 12 => Tunnel waypoint FLY direct; only trajectory points no LINE draw
# 40 => Tunnel waypoint FLY-BY (radius_meter = value for pitch)
# 41 => Tunnel waypoint FLY-BY (radius_meter = value for pitch) no RECTANGLE draw
# 42 => Tunnel waypoint FLY-BY (radius_meter = value for pitch) no LINE draw
# 90 => end of data; start updating Tunnel on Plugin side
# 99 => delete all stored Tunnel Data in Plugin
